con:config.con:query: SELECT s.PRO_NB,sli.[Pieces_QT] ,sli.[Packaging_Type_CD] ,s.Shipment_key, s.WGP_Record_Key from SHIP.Shipment_VW s left outer join [SHIP].[Shipment_Line_Item_VW] sli on (sli.[Shipment_KEY] = s.[Shipment_KEY] ) where s.PRO_NB = '${SpreadSheet#PRO}' and (sli.[Packaging_Type_CD] is not null or sli.[Pieces_QT] is not null) order by sli.[Pieces_QT] desc

select m.[WGP_ID_NBR], m.WGP_SHP_TAG ,sli.[SLI_NBR_PCS] , sli.[SLI_PKG_CD],m.Record_key from Legacy.M204_SLI sli left outer join Legacy.M204_WGP m on (sli.[SLI_SHP_TAG] = m.WGP_SHP_TAG and (sli.[SLI_PKG_CD] is not null or sli.[SLI_NBR_PCS] is not null)) where WGP_ID_NBR = '${SpreadSheet#PRO}' order by sli.[SLI_NBR_PCS] desc
